review:
I would like to write about Arya Dentals. I went to Arya Dentals for Teeth whitening and Cleaning.

Dr.Kiran is an excellent Dentist who listens to the patient and explains everything very well.

I Recommend Dr.Kiran Kumar, Arya Dentals Team, and Arya Dentals. He is the Best Dentist I have ever seen.

Treatment is satisfactory
Explanation of health issues is good
Less waiting time

review: It was sooo normal and too cool while communicating with the Doctor he was sooo friendly in nature and explained the issues or treatment I need to take in a simple manner where I can understand it easily. And the treatment was very good. I strongly recommend the Dr to my family members and friends. And even i came through strong recommendations from my family people who already took treatment from Doctor Nagabandi Kiran Kumar sir. Over all it was a good and best experience. Thank you sir.
reply_text: Thank you so much. Ur appreciation added more responsibility.
